(XML Line 000104): Hanging paragraph in clause
	<clause id="_9" obligation="normative"><p id="_08cc68ee-8c7b-4ae9-9a84-ce5106b0dece">Nominations are solicited exclusively from producers of CRMs and developer/owners of RMM/Ps
	The Secretariat announces an open solicitation for nominations of CRMs and RMM/Ps for inclusion in the JCTLM database of available materials and methods/procedures of a higher metrological order. The solicitation is made each year from February to the end of May. The solicitation announcement is found on the website of the BIPM at : <link target="https://www.bipm.org/en/committees/jc/jctlm/jctlm-nominations-and-review.html"/></p>
	<clause id="_10" obligation="normative"><p id="_eb5045af-3301-4b63-9c6e-ec61b28743c1">A fixed date for receiving completed nominations will be specified in the announcement. Nominations received after the date specified in the solicitation announcement may be deferred for review in a subsequent review cycle.</p>
	<clause id="_11" obligation="normative">
	
(XML Line 000106): Hanging paragraph in clause
	<clause id="_10" obligation="normative"><p id="_eb5045af-3301-4b63-9c6e-ec61b28743c1">A fixed date for receiving completed nominations will be specified in the announcement. Nominations received after the date specified in the solicitation announcement may be deferred for review in a subsequent review cycle.</p>
	<clause id="_11" obligation="normative">
	
	<p id="_99be8b16-b1b2-434f-8896-a9de186f9945">The deadline for submitting nominations is 30<sup>th</sup> May. In the case of reference method nominations, the submission deadline remains 30<sup>th</sup> May, but it is possible to submit the final version (non-changeable format) of its supporting documentation or publication by the 30<sup>th</sup> September.</p>
	</clause></clause>
(XML Line 000117): Hanging paragraph in clause
	<clause id="_13" obligation="normative"><p id="_1fa840f8-2e7c-4608-b200-2cec953d885c">Submitting Nomination Forms for consideration by the DB WG:</p>
	<clause id="_14" obligation="normative">
	
	<p id="_f5868fdf-afd2-49ae-9afd-40284e84144b">Nominating forms must be submitted by email to the JCTLM Secretariat at <link target="mailto:jctlm@bipm.org"/>. Additional information and instructions for completing the forms are found on the BIPM website at <link target="https://www.bipm.org/utils/common/pdf/JCTLM/DBWG-P-02A-I-01.pdf"/></p>
	</clause>
